OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FEngland fans remain confident the
OL,7,FThree Lions will go far in the World
OL,8,FCup despite a "rather unexciting" 2-0
OL,9,Fwin over Panama.
OL,11,FSecond-half goals from Jude Bellingham
OL,12,Fand Harry Kane sealed top spot in
OL,13,Ftheir group, meaning they will play in
OL,14,FAtlanta for the first round of the
OL,15,Fknockout stages on Wednesday.
OL,17,FSupporters were forced to endure heavy
OL,18,Frain ahead of kick-off at the MetLife
OL,19,FStadium in New Jersey on Saturday `
OL,20,Fwith many wearing ponchos and holding
OL,21,Fumbrellas.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@aO]
