OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FThe mood of the England faithful was
OL,7,Fnot improved by a frustrating goalless
OL,8,Ffirst half.
OL,10,FCommenting on the first half, one fan
OL,11,Fwho has tickets for England's round of
OL,12,F32 fixture, which is likely to be
OL,13,Fagainst either Senegal or the
OL,14,FDemocratic Republic of Congo, said it
OL,15,Fleft him thinking: "Do I really want
OL,16,Fto spend 500 bucks... to watch that?"
OL,26,@wD@TOUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
