OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FAdam Alfandary, 39, originally from
OL,7,FLondon but now living in New York,
OL,8,Ftold the Press Association: "It was
OL,9,Frather unexciting, but we won. We've
OL,10,Ftopped the group.
OL,12,F"I'm supposed to be going to Atlanta
OL,13,Fon Wednesday ` I don't know if I can
OL,14,Fmake it because of work but I hope I
OL,15,Fcan.
OL,17,F"I've got the tickets, I don't know if
OL,18,FI'm going to sell them or I'm going to
OL,19,Fkeep them."
OL,26,@pD@]OUtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
