OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FAsked how he was feeling during the
OL,7,Ffirst half, he said: "I was thinking,
OL,8,Fdo I really want to spend 500 bucks to
OL,9,Ffly to Atlanta to watch that? But I
OL,10,Fthink I will."
OL,12,FQuestioned on what he thought of
OL,13,FEngland's chances in the tournament,
OL,14,Fhe told PA: "With that defence, I'd be
OL,15,Fhappy if we got to the round of 16 `
OL,16,Fthe round of 16 in the Azteca, that's
OL,17,Fwhat I'm looking forward to."
OL,26,@oD@VOUrD@NO]vD@MOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
