OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FTom Mayers, 46, who is originally from
OL,7,FWest London but now lives in the US,
OL,8,Ftold PA: "It was a great result for
OL,9,FEngland ` they did the business.
OL,11,F"Harry Kane popped up with a header
OL,12,Fand job done. Onto the last 32.
OL,14,F"This has kind of cleaned me out going
OL,15,Fto see this so we'll probably be down
OL,16,Fthe pub to see the last 32."
OL,26,@pD@JOUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
