OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FCommenting on England's chances for
OL,7,Fthe rest of the tournament, Mr Mayers
OL,8,Fsaid: "Improving, I still think
OL,9,Fthey've got some work to do but I'm
OL,10,Fgetting more confident.
OL,12,F"Once you get to the knockout stages
OL,13,Fanything can happen ` you've got Harry
OL,14,FKane up front so who knows."
OL,16,FAnother supporter said he wished the
OL,17,Fgame against Panama had been better
OL,18,Fbecause "I spent a lot of money on my
OL,19,Fticket".
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUvD@\O]zD@IOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
