OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FPaul Cotterill, 58, who is originally
OL,7,Ffrom Basildon in Essex but now lives
OL,8,Fin New Jersey, said: "It was pretty
OL,9,Fmuch what I expected ` as long as we
OL,10,Fwon that was all that really mattered.
OL,12,F"I didn't think much of it to be
OL,13,Fhonest with you, I wish it had been a
OL,14,Fbit better. I spent a lot of money on
OL,15,Fmy ticket."
OL,26,@pD@VOUtD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
