OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FAsked for his thoughts on how England
OL,7,Fwould do in the tournament, Mr
OL,8,FCotterill added: "What are my hopes?
OL,9,FYes, it's coming home. We're going to
OL,10,Fwin ` absolutely, I love it. It's
OL,11,Fcoming home 100%."
OL,13,FMany England fans said the game
OL,14,Fagainst Panama was tougher than they
OL,15,Fexpected.
OL,17,FAlex Addison, 38, from London, said
OL,18,FPanama "looked better" but added:
OL,19,F"We're out of the group... life goes
OL,20,Fon".
OL,26,@pD@ROUsD@RO]zD@HOUzD@VO]{D@AOU|D@CO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
