OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FHe said: "It was good. It was a battle
OL,7,Fin the first half but they looked like
OL,8,Fthey were going to create.
OL,10,F"Then finally they pulled through and
OL,11,Fcreated the chance and bang ` a couple
OL,12,Fof goals and everyone is happy.
OL,14,F"To be fair I think Panama should have
OL,15,Fscored ` they looked better than we
OL,16,Fdid.
OL,18,F"But we're out of the group, top of
OL,19,Fthe group, life goes on."
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
