OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782616677
OL,3,CEngland fans remain confident despite
OL,4,C'unexciting' Panama win
OL,6,FAsked if he was going to the match in
OL,7,FAtlanta for the round of 32, Mr
OL,8,FAddison said: "For myself, I would
OL,9,Flove to, but I've got a flight home
OL,10,Ftomorrow and then I'd love to come
OL,11,Fback ` maybe not the next round but in
OL,12,Fa couple of rounds.
OL,14,F"We're going all the way, its coming
OL,15,Fhome."
